  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Elesham\" title=\"House Elesham\"><img alt=\"House Elesham.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/0/0d/House_Elesham.svg/50px-House_Elesham.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/0/0d/House_Elesham.svg/75px-House_Elesham.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/0/0d/House_Elesham.svg/100px-House_Elesham.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\">Lord Elesham</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Elesham\" title=\"House Elesham\"><img alt=\"House Elesham.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/0/0d/House_Elesham.svg/50px-House_Elesham.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/0/0d/House_Elesham.svg/75px-House_Elesham.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/0/0d/House_Elesham.svg/100px-House_Elesham.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_the_Paps\" title=\"Lord of the Paps\">Lord of the Paps</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc41.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc41.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Elesham\" title=\"House Elesham\">House Elesham</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Valemen\" title=\"Valemen\">Valemen</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Spouse</th><td>\nA daughter of <a href=\"/index.php/Elys_Waynwood\" title=\"Elys Waynwood\">Elys Waynwood</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc41.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc41.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Lord Elesham</b> was a Lord of the <a href=\"/index.php/Paps\" title=\"Paps\">Paps</a> and a head of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Elesham\" title=\"House Elesham\">House Elesham</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc41.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc41.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lord_Elesham&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Lord Elesham wed a daughter of Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Elys_Waynwood\" title=\"Elys Waynwood\">Elys Waynwood</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Alys_Arryn\" title=\"Alys Arryn\">Alys Arryn</a>. Their <a href=\"/index.php/Marriage\" title=\"Marriage\">marriage</a> produces no children, however.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc41.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc41.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lord_Elesham&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon g